      <title>美国至少在五月份每月购买石油作为战略储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-to-buy-oil-for-strategic-reserve-monthly-through-at-least-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着拜登政府继续实施目前接近 40 年来最低水平的洞穴回填计划，美国计划至少在 5 月份举行每月招标，为其战略石油储备购买石油。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-08/us-to-buy-oil-for-strategic-reserve-monthly-through-at-least-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 15:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
